Package: morphospace
Title: Build and Visualize Multivariate Ordinations of Shape Data
Version: 0.0.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Pablo", family = "Milla Carmona", email = "pablomillac@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
         comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0396-6244"))
Description: Build and visualize multivariate ordinations of shape data resulting from 
    geometric morphometrics analyses, including tools for filtering morphometric 
    signal, projecting different elements into morphospace, and combining shape 
    variables with non-shape data.
